io.sarl.lang.core

Class Agent

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sarl.lang.core.SRESpecificDataContainer
      • io.sarl.lang.core.AgentProtectedAPIObject
        • io.sarl.lang.core.Agent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable

    public class Agent
extends AgentProtectedAPIObject
implements Identifiable
    The definition of the notion of Agent in SARL. An agent is an autonomous entity having some intrinsic skills to realize the capacities it exhibits. An agent defines a context.
    Version:
    0.7.0-SNAPSHOT 2017-10-05 16:27:23
